umns: 1fr; }\nindex.html:152:      .hero-proof { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\nindex.html:154:      .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\nindex.html:298:          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 18px;\">The answers are written to be useful without promising facts this demo company has not verified.</p>\n","isError":false}

